      • direct_one_curve

        @Test
public void direct_one_curve()
        Calibrate a single curve to 4 points. Use the resulting calibrated curves as starting point of the computation of a Jacobian. Compare the direct Jacobian and the one reconstructed from trades.

      • with_rebucketing_one_curve

        @Test
public void with_rebucketing_one_curve()
        Start from a generic zero-coupon curve. Compute the (inverse) Jacobian matrix using linear projection to a small number of points and the Jacobian utility. Compare the direct Jacobian obtained by calibrating a curve based on the trades with market quotes computed from the zero-coupon curve.
